  // leaf on annotated (i32, i64, i32, i64, i32, i64) -> i64 calls in the
  // canonical i64 zero-test self-select. A mismatch in any logical slot retains
  // both calls. Source: `OptimizeInstructions.cpp:2891-2947`; oracle:
